50|$|The Wolfendens {{were another}} foreign family {{who went into}} exile in Lambeg and {{assisted}} in the establishing of the manufacture of <b>linen</b> <b>cloth</b> in the village. They are buried in Lambeg graveyard. The bridge over the River Lagan is still referred to as Wolfenden's Bridge.|$|R
